'''威爾斯蛋糕'''（{{lang-cy|Picau ar y maen、Cacen gri或是Teisen gri}}）是一種外觀為小圓餅模樣，裡面參雜著[[葡萄乾|葡萄乾]]、[[桑特醋栗|桑特醋栗]]之類乾果，起源自19世紀的[[威爾斯|威爾斯]]傳統點心<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/welsh_cakes_16706 |title=Traditional Welsh cakes |work=[[BBC|BBC]] |author=Mary Hamilton |date= |accessdate=2020-11-27 |archive-date=2020-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206034156/https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/welsh_cakes_16706 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title=Encyclopaedia of Wales |author=John Davies、Nigel Jenkins、Menna Baines、Peredur I. Lynch |publisher=University of Wales Press |date=2008-01-31 |isbn=978-070-8-31953-6 |page=931頁}}</ref>。

在製作方法上，威爾斯蛋糕主要使用麵粉、奶油、雞蛋、牛奶來作成麵糊，再加上乾果、香料與糖<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.visitwales.com/things-do/food-and-drink/welsh-food/traditional-welsh-cakes-recipe |title=Make your own delicious Welsh cakes |work=Visit Wales |accessdate=2020-11-27 |archive-date=2021-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301151055/https://www.visitwales.com/things-do/food-and-drink/welsh-food/traditional-welsh-cakes-recipe |dead-url=no }}</ref>。因為威爾斯蛋糕是放在烤盤或烘烤板上烘烤，在威爾斯當地也將此稱呼為烤盤蛋糕<ref name="NewsWales">{{cite web |url=http://www.newswales.co.uk/index.cfm?id=10569 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140811055146/http://www.newswales.co.uk/index.cfm?id=10569 |dead-url=yes |title=Fast facts about Welsh cakes - and a recipe |work=News Wales |date=2007-02-07 |archive-date=2014-08-11 |accessdate=2020-11-27 }}</ref>。另外在[[格拉摩根|格拉摩根]]一帶，也有採用[[荷蘭鍋|荷蘭鍋]]來烘烤威爾斯蛋糕的料理方法<ref name="NewsWales"/>。

威爾斯人常將威爾斯蛋糕做為搭配[[下午茶|下午茶]]的甜點，也會在[[聖大衛日|聖大衛日]]之類傳統節慶上食用<ref name="NewsWales"/>。

